   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the 4th year of our lord Probus Augustus, on Pauni [. .], has paid Nilos son of Ptolemaios, of Karanis, 32 drachmai (for) the monthly (anabolikon). I, Apolias, son of Aurelius Isidoros, have signed.</ab>
